{"tid":2409899,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄧炳強避答衝鋒槍cut單「研用低殺傷力武器」","createTime":"2021-02-16T07:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T07:58:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d1b29b9e0d853095c2cdd06315055c01bcd45e83","tid":2409899,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:25:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210216/MSI46ZOFJ5DPXOJCRVLL24YNAI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210216%2FMSI46ZOFJ5DPXOJCRVLL24YNAI%2F&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bliy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=85071753\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210216%2FMSI46ZOFJ5DPXOJCRVLL24YNAI%2F&h=0c09a2ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210216/MSI46ZOFJ5DPXOJCRVLL24YNAI/</a><br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強避答衝鋒槍cut單「研用低殺傷力武器」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-a8fuiArPdHbjgfH-6iXxrP0dlE=/921x518/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZXU5DIH7XBADFCQKDJYKTJ7WKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-a8fuiArPdHbjgfH-6iXxrP0dlE%3D%2F921x518%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZXU5DIH7XBADFCQKDJYKTJ7WKE.jpg&h=af4640a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鄧炳強稱正研究真槍以外的低武力選擇。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港警隊在反送中運動中濫暴，劣迹斑斑，遭歐美各國禁運武器，其中警隊早前訂購美國SIG廠製造的衝鋒槍便因禁運被迫取消定單，要向其他國家尋求購置槍械。 警務處長鄧炳強昨到長洲視察時，未有否認警隊是否要向其他國家訂購槍械，亦無回應是否計劃添置電槍，只承認正研究使用不同低殺傷力武器。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強昨乘坐水警輪抵達長洲巡視，並。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民權觀察促解釋必要性<br />\n<br />\n民權觀察發言人沈偉男表示，外國曾出現因警員使用電槍而造成傷亡的例子，認為警方已配備不同的非致命性武器，用於大型示威或警員執勤時控制場面，若再引入電槍，需解釋必要性。<br />\n<br />\n民權觀察質疑警方以往在使用武力時並無恪守最低武力原則，目前亦未清楚有何警員將配備電槍，加上警方並無公開武力使用準則，擔心日後如果有警員使用電槍，公眾不容易監察。"},{"pid":"aa446516358ff2692146b9c58793f43cdf979d5f","tid":2409899,"uid":300782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy